    "body": "Perhaps I misunderstand how `axis` works on `groupby`, but something seems wrong here:\r\n```\r\ndf = pd.DataFrame({'a': [1, 1, 2, 2], 'b': [2,2,4,4], 'c':[1,1,1,1]})\r\n```\r\nThis `df.groupby('a', axis=1).apply(lambda x: x.loc['b'].sum())`, produces an empty dataframe.\r\n\r\nCompare that to `df.apply(lambda x: x.loc['b'].sum(), axis=1)`:\r\n```\r\n0    2\r\n1    2\r\n2    4\r\n3    4\r\ndtype: int64\r\n```"
